    "Description": "Guess some folks just can\u2019t dogfight. Sent a young prospect out on patrol, and am now being barraged with comms about how they\u2019re barely hanging on. Had them update me with the details about who they\u2019re up against and I damn near fell outta my chair laughing.    \n\nIf this kid can\u2019t handle a People\u2019s Alliance ship, they sure ain\u2019t ready for flight assignments. Appreciate it if you could save their hide anyway.\n\nIf you\u2019re free, could you head over to <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> and show \u2018em how it\u2019s done?\n\n-Stows",
